window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Bastard’s Eve is a night of celebration for most residents in the canal city of Lodi - but not for sorcerer Learned Penric and his Temple demon Desdemona, who find themselves caught up in the affairs of a shiplost madman, a dangerous ascendant demon, and a very unexpected saint of the fifth god.</p> <p>This novella falls between <i>Penric’s Fox</i> and <i>Penric’s Mission</i> in the internal chronology of the Penric &amp; Desdemona tales.</p>"; 
